><br />\n要 我果時考0905 勁好考<br />\n考靠背壟<br />\n冇晒校巴 街上冇車咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba42b90fa98632d6919a98aac6634da2bf1d519","tid":289202,"uid":2020,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:01:38.000Z","msg":"多數轉左嫁喇 返放學時段就多d望行人路，動作要大d<br />\n<br />\n記得同出面企街姐姐傾幾句 佢會幫你係試場開路出車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次佢成個人閘係馬路比我慢慢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一個燈位如果綠燈去唔切就慢慢渣到佢轉紅啦<br />\n<br />\n入到靠背壟就多d望行人路，會有老人家同細路突然彈出黎，呢段要慢慢黎，安心至上<br />\n<br />\n內街出返靠背壟就望清楚d先好去，果個位都係易肥位。<br />\n<br />\n返試場條直路我師傅話可以上一上三波，cut返右線時落返2波同打燈睇的士同小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大致係咁 如果果日落細雨重好 你係靠背壟有得睇遮知有無人想亂過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我考果時落大雨加放哂學 條路一架車都無 好似私人賽道咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d32f7935675337b5a99f65f64500a4bb0a80e3","tid":289202,"uid":73123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天光道轉右就易</blockquote><br />\n轉右上到頂先見到下面燈位俾車頂死，停左黃格就897"},{"pid":"6f02e9010cd92244d6c29df846ad81107e50d96e","tid":289202,"uid":58774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天光道 1take pass <br />\n校巴時間可以預定重考<br />\nbtw加油 <br />\n小心睇燈 唔好沖左上黃格仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n感謝師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f06154fd7d54ee49f7c070f8a81fdbcd88b4d9","tid":289202,"uid":58774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T06:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天光道唔係難過永考街咩？</blockquote><br />\n我個人覺得永考難d"},{"pid":"d48acc0b745c0c62a2ada6e852dd651a97571671","tid":289202,"uid":58774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T06:04:02.000Z","msg":