 />\n第一個燈位如果綠燈去唔切就慢慢渣到佢轉紅啦<br />\n<br />\n入到靠背壟就多d望行人路，會有老人家同細路突然彈出黎，呢段要慢慢黎，安心至上<br />\n<br />\n內街出返靠背壟就望清楚d先好去，果個位都係易肥位。<br />\n<br />\n返試場條直路我師傅話可以上一上三波，cut返右線時落返2波同打燈睇的士同小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大致係咁 如果果日落細雨重好 你係靠背壟有得睇遮知有無人想亂過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我考果時落大雨加放哂學 條路一架車都無 好似私人賽道咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n感謝您大絲！ 希望考11點時無乜校車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n11點無校車呀"},{"pid":"22a7c5630214ff113c94c6f95eadd3d7e31c36a9","tid":289202,"uid":87839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"考1535是咪可以準備定510<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9839f1a10bb4c97ef2e1178a82a5085dcf53709c","tid":289202,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"考完就報告下"},{"pid":"08a041dd44b448aae928c455b21a399ce1af473e","tid":289202,"uid":91331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搶到731朝早0855建唔建議要<br />\n求建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要 我果時考0905 勁好考<br />\n考靠背壟<br />\n冇晒校巴 街上冇車咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390f5eee2ff02937e3d121fc416d4fc9c7246b28","tid":289202,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:39:41.000Z","msg":"永考定忠孝呀"},{"pid":"818b91b15d9cca73e85831a440a13c1a1677e2f8","tid":289202,"uid":1538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考過天光肥左<br />\n果日斜路起步條路左邊泊曬車接放學<br />\n得番燈位前個半車位無人泊<i